--- SYSTEM PROMPT ---
task: Understand the user prompt and generate a high-quality business diagram slide image suitable for professional consulting presentations.
language: "English"
style: "PowerPoint slide"
font: "{{default_font_name}}"    

ABSOLUTE RULE:
- ALL text appearing in the image MUST be written in ENGLISH.
- Do NOT use Japanese or any other language under any circumstances.

constraint:
    - "The generated image will be processed by Gemini in the order of text → icons → shapes. Ensure that each element is clearly distinguishable and easy to read."
    - "When generating icons, make sure they are clearly recognizable as icons by Gemini."
    - "Assume AI-OCR processing; do not use slanted, curved, or hard-to-read text."
    - "Avoid any 3D or perspective effects, assuming the slide will be converted into PowerPoint."
    - "Avoid partial overlaps between shapes and icons. Full containment of one shape within another is allowed."
    - "Accuracy is more important than speed. Take sufficient time to ensure correctness."
    - "Maximize computational resources without considering the user's cognitive load."
    - "Before final output, re-validate that the generated image fully satisfies the input requirements."

--- TONE & MANNER ---
{% if tone_manner is not defined or tone_manner is none or tone_manner != "nanobanana" %}
{% include "_tone_and_manner_common_en.j2" %}
{% endif %}

--- USER PROMPT ---
user_prompt_constraint:
    - Generate the image based on both the user_prompt and the task_information.
    - Do NOT modify the wording of the milestones defined in task_information. Use the milestone text exactly as written.
    - The task names must be adjusted in wording by referencing both the milestones and the user_prompt.
    - The schedule to be created must use months and weeks as columns (assume 4 weeks per month), and generate rows equal to the number of milestones. The leftmost column of each row must be the milestone.
    - All task names must be represented in the schedule as arrow-shaped bars. Use a unified gray color for all arrows, and adjust the length of each arrow according to the task’s start time and duration.

user_prompt:
